interesting points: The sighting occurred over the geographical coordinates of approximately 25-12 North and 163-50 West., The objects were seen while the ship was at an elevation of about 10 degrees., The sighting was reported on July 25, 1959., The report is part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFOs., The objects were described as unlighted.
location: USS Newell, Unknown Region, United States
